      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2003 BMW M3, a quintessential driver's machine powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit features individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Critical enthusiast maintenance has been addressed, including a Vanos system refresh and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to maintain structural rigidity. The chassis benefits from a limited-slip differential and a well-sorted suspension geometry that provides excellent linear feedback and turn-in precision. While showing signs of respectful use, the drivetrain remains robust, offering the raw, analog performance characteristic of the E46 platform. A turn-key example for the purist looking for peak naturally aspirated engineering.",
